# Kubernetes Namespace Task

## Objective

Setup Minikube locally and create a Kubernetes Namespace.

## Requirements

- Docker Desktop
- WSL2
- kubectl
- Minikube

## Steps

1. Start Minikube
2. Verify Cluster
3. Create Namespace
4. Verify Namespace
5. Describe Namespace
6. Delete Namespace

## Commands

minikube start --driver=docker

kubectl get nodes

kubectl apply -f namespace.yaml

kubectl get namespaces

kubectl describe namespace demo-namespace

kubectl delete namespace demo-namespace
